                     the German with an Introduction by Edwin
                        Björkman\pwindex{Bjoerkman, Edwin@\textsc{Björkman, Edwin} (19.\,10.\,1866 Stockholm – 16.\,11.\,1951 Asheville), \emph{Schriftsteller, Übersetzer, Publizist}|pwk}. New York: \emph{Mitchell Kennerley}\orgindex{Mitchell Kennerley@Mitchell Kennerley|pwk}{ }1915.}}}\label{KT105-1h} of three of his characteristic efforts has been published in this
