           \noindent{}You look at this city and regretfully wonder. Was there ever a Vienna of the Strauss\pwindex{Strauss, Johann@\textsc{Strauss, Johann}, gen. \textsc{Sohn} (25.\,10.\,1825 Wien – 3.\,6.\,1899 ebd.), \emph{Komponist, Dirigent}|pw} waltzes?
