           \pagebreak[2] 
               {\centering\pstart[\vspace{0.35\baselineskip}]\noindent\leftskip=3em plus1fill\rightskip\leftskip
            Careless of Life\pend[\vspace{0.15\baselineskip}]}\nopagebreak[4] \pstart
           \noindent{}»I recall a simple, quite unimportant incident, but it is so characteristic that I
