           \noindent{}\emph{Arthur Schnitzler, Viennese
                  playwright and novelist, an interview with whom is reported below by Karl
                  Scheuermann, a Milwaukee newspaper\orgindex{Milwaukee Newspaper Union@Milwaukee Newspaper Union|pw} man, is one of
